Class Auxiliary

  • java.lang.Object
    • optional.lab2.Auxiliary

  • public class Auxiliary
extends java.lang.Object
    Auxiliary is an additional class to store the supplies and demands line per line It consists of :
    • A supply for a source
    • A demand for a destination
    • A value that stores the cost from a source to destination
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Dmitri Cojocari
